{{Infobox company | name = Banque internationale à Luxembourg | logo = BIL LOGO WIKIPEDIA.JPG | type = | industry = | fate = | predecessor = <!-- or: | predecessors = --> | successor = <!-- or: | successors = --> | founded = <!-- if known: {{Start date and age|YYYY|MM|DD}} in [[city]], [[state]], [[country]] --> | founder = <!-- or: | founders = --> | defunct = <!-- {{End date|YYYY|MM|DD}} --> | hq_location_city = | hq_location_country = | area_served = <!-- or: | areas_served = --> | key_people = | products = | owner = <!-- or: | owners = --> | num_employees = | num_employees_year = <!-- Year of num_employees data (if known) --> | parent = | website = <!-- {{URL|example.com}} --> }}
'''Banque Internationale à Luxembourg S.A.''' (BIL) is a Luxembourgish bank. It is the oldest private bank in Luxembourg.<ref name="veconomist" >{{cite news|author=|title=A Chinese carmaker agrees to buy a Danish investment bank|url=https://www.economist.com/news/finance-and-economics/21730048-despite-curbs-outward-investment-chinese-firms-are-expanding-european|work=[[The Economist]]|date=5 October 2017}}</ref> The bank is owned by [[Legend Holdings]] (89.936%) and the [[Luxembourg]] government (9.993%).
==History== Found in 1856, the bank was a major bank of Luxembourg. It was acquired by [[Dexia]] in 1999.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://actions.trends.levif.be/actions/trends/manager-de-lannee/files/2006-axel-miller.pdf|title=Manager de l'Année|website=Levif.be|date=11 January 2007|author=Sébastien Buron|language=fr|accessdate=12 September 2017}}</ref> In 2012 Dexia sold BIL for €730&nbsp;million to [[Precision Capital]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.dexia.com/EN/journalist/press_releases/Documents/20121005_Closing%20BIL_EN.pdf|title=Closing of the sale of Banque Internationale à Luxembourg|date=5 October 2012|access-date=13 April 2016|publisher=Dexia}}</ref>
In 2017 [[Legend Holdings]] acquired the bank from Precision Capital for €1.484&nbsp;billion.<ref>{{cite press release|url=https://www.bil.com/en/bil-group/pressroom/news/Pages/legend-holdings-to-acquire-precision-capital-stake-in-bil.aspx|title=Legend Holdings to acquire Precision Capital's stake in Banque Internationale à Luxembourg|date=1 September 2017|access-date=3 September 2017|publisher=Banque Internationale à Luxembourg}}</ref><ref>{{cite press release|url=http://www.hkexnews.hk/listedco/listconews/SEHK/2017/0901/LTN201709012275.pdf|title=Major Transaction Acquisition of 89.936% Issued Share Capital in Banque Internationale a Luxembourg S.A. |date=1 September 2017|access-date=3 September 2017|publisher=Legend Holdings}}</ref>
