{{Orphan|date=February 2009}} '''Hai Au Paper JSC''' (CTCP Giấy Hải Âu; [[Hanoi Securities Trading Center|HASTC]]:GHA) is a [[paper]] company in [[Vietnam]]. It is a [[subsidiary company]] of HAPACO (Hanoi Paper Company) and is listed on the [[Hanoi Securities Trading Center]]. Hai Au is active in the paper sector, producing [[packaging material]] and [[forestry]] supplies, and trading paper goods and goods involved in the paper industry. It is located in [[Hai Phong]].<ref>[https://www.google.com/finance?q=HST%3AGHA Google finance, Hai Au Paper JSC]</ref>
