{{Infobox recurring event | name = IDEF International Defence Industry Fair | native_name = IDEF Uluslararası Savunma Sanayi Fuarı | native_name_lang = | logo = | logo_alt = | logo_caption = | logo_size = | image = IDEF2015 (2).JPG | image_size = 200 | alt = | caption = IDEF'15 held in May 2015 at TÜYAP Fair Ground, [[Istanbul]]. | status = Active | genre = Fair | date = <!-- {{start date|YYYY|mm|dd}} "dates=" also works, but do not use both --> | begins = <!-- {{start date|YYYY|mm|dd}} --> | ends = <!-- {{start date|YYYY|mm|dd}} --> | frequency = Bi-annually | venue = | location = | coordinates = <!-- {{coord|LAT|LON|type:event|display=inline,title}} --> | country = Turkey | first = 1993 | founder_name = Turkish Armed Forces Foundation | last = {{End date|2015|05|08|df=y}} | prev = 2013 | next = 2017 | participants = 820 companies from 51 Countries | attendance = 65,782 Visitors from 116 Countries | capacity = | area = 120,000 m2, 12 halls | budget = | activity = | leader_name = | patron = | organised = <!-- "organized=" also works --> | filing = | people = | member = | sponsor = | website = [http://idef.com.tr/en/ IDEF] | footnotes = }}
[[File:FNSS PARS Frontside.JPG|thumb|200px|An [[FNSS Pars]] [[8x8]] [[armoured personnel carrier]] at the IDEF 2007 fair in [[Ankara]].]]
The '''International Defence Industry Fair (IDEF)''' is a [[defence industry]] [[fair]] held in [[Turkey]] and organized by the [[Turkish Armed Forces|Turkish Armed Forces Foundation]] since 1993.<ref name=TSKGV>[http://www.tskgv.org.tr/tskgv/?p=1713&lang=en Turkish Armed Forces Foundation: IDEF]</ref> The Foundation organizes the IDEF once in every two years and before each fair it chooses the organizer firm and exhibition venue by calling a tender.<ref name=TSKGV/> The exhibitions generally take place in [[Ankara]] or [[Istanbul]].<ref name=TSKGV/>
IDEF International Defence Industry Fair has been held once in every odd year since 1993.
IDEF, as a high technology defence industry fair, incorporating main defence industry branches and their subordinates, is an essential international marketing arena for defence industry companies. IDEF is the biggest defence industry fair in Eurasian region and one of the top four in the world with an increasing trend in terms of the number of participating countries, delegations and companies.<ref name="IDEF'17">[http://www.idef.com.tr/en/index.php?main=hakkinda IDEF Official Web Site]</ref>
==See also== * [[Saha Expo]], Defense, Aviation and Aerospace Fair in Istanbul
