Electrocentrale Bucharest owns three [[subsidiary|subsidiaries]] with a total installed capacity of 2,008 [[Watt#Megawatt|MW]] and an annual average power production of 6.759 [[TWh]], which is 12.7% of the total national output of [[Romania]]. {{cn|date=August 2017}}
